{"tid":885823,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"加速世界入面個Graphite Edge係咪桐人嚟?","createTime":"2018-11-01T15:27:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-02T00:37:43.000Z","uid":209097,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5e19ae95f623f920563d89fae1182acfd5c2ec5d","tid":885823,"uid":209097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T15:27:16.000Z","msg":"兩個衣著都係全黑為主。<br />\nGraphite Edge：<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/txBvtch.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtxBvtch.png&h=689abd23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n桐人：<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MUcbcD8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMUcbcD8.png&h=72378bbf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n武器方面，大家都係用兩把劍。<br />\n<br />\n技能方面：Graphite Edge係加速世界入面用過Vertical Square 同 Slant，依兩招都係黎自SAO入面嘅劍技。而Graphite Edge係加速世界入面試過用劍劈子彈。亦有可以可以將任何事物都切碎嘅技能。再加上，黑雪姬講過佢之所以識用星爆氣流斬，係Graphite Edge教佢。<br />\n<br />\n個人方面，Graphite Edge平時好輕浮，但係重要嘅時候就好冷靜沈穩，同桐人一樣。而且Graphite Edge以前送過一樣可以hack入全世界所有server嘅apps比黑雪姬睇同改自己個人資料，反映出佢同桐人一樣hacker技術好高超。<br />\n<br />\n再加上，Graphite Edge個配音係松岡。<br />\n<br />\n所以佢地會唔會係同一個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bd13b5d9e1702a0808fbf5b177ed85e56b831b3","tid":885823,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T23:59:40.000Z","msg":"一定唔係"},{"pid":"4e978f5446d12aefcc48f94fe827888c3c8fd7fc","tid":885823,"uid":160234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T00:37:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}